00:28:01.230 --> 00:28:04.720 align:middle line:84%
The other one is a stream of
energy, of matter, coming out.

00:28:04.720 --> 00:28:05.520 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: OK.

00:28:05.520 --> 00:28:08.910 align:middle line:84%
>>ADAIR: And it tries to
stretch out towards Earth,

00:28:08.910 --> 00:28:11.175 align:middle line:84%
but the gravity field of
the sun is so intense,

00:28:11.175 --> 00:28:13.620 align:middle line:84%
it pulls that back and it
makes that circle that you

00:28:13.620 --> 00:28:15.190 align:middle line:90%
see, a loop coming off the sun.

00:28:15.190 --> 00:28:15.990 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Mhm.

00:28:15.990 --> 00:28:18.270 align:middle line:84%
>>ADAIR: And we call
the a "prominence."

00:28:18.270 --> 00:28:20.850 align:middle line:84%
