00:32:43.310 --> 00:32:45.830 align:middle line:10%
And with transportation
knocked down by the attack,

00:32:45.830 --> 00:32:47.810 align:middle line:10%
that prolongs the isolation.

00:32:47.810 --> 00:32:49.775 align:middle line:90%
Brian Todd, CNN, Washington.

00:32:49.775 --> 00:32:51.280 align:middle line:90%
