They're told to retaliate.

00:35:26.030 --> 00:35:26.870 align:middle line:90%
>>ADAIR: Yeah.

00:35:26.870 --> 00:35:27.890 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: That's scary.

00:35:27.890 --> 00:35:28.931 align:middle line:90%
>>ADAIR: It's terrifying.

00:35:28.931 --> 00:35:31.650 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: A mistake
could ruin the planet.

00:35:31.650 --> 00:35:32.450 align:middle line:90%
>>ADAIR: Exactly.

00:35:32.450 --> 00:35:34.550 align:middle line:84%
We're lucky we-- we're so
lucky through the years

00:35:34.550 --> 00:35:37.120 align:middle line:90%
