your world forever.

00:35:45.860 --> 00:35:46.660 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: EMPs.

00:35:46.660 --> 00:35:47.930 align:middle line:90%
>>ADAIR: YEP.

00:35:47.930 --> 00:35:52.670 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Electromagnetic pulse,
an attack in the atmosphere.

00:35:52.670 --> 00:35:54.680 align:middle line:90%
