>>ADAIR: Right.

00:36:17.750 --> 00:36:19.208 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: It's like
a domino effect.

00:36:19.208 --> 00:36:22.520 align:middle line:84%
>>ADAIR: There are-- there
